Install openvpn aws


Spin up a free tier ubuntu 22.04 server

sudo apt update
sudo apt upgrade
sudo apt autoremove
sudo apt autoclean

wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Nyr/openvpn-install/master/openvpn-install.sh -O ubuntu-22.04-lts-vpn-server.sh

make the downloaded file executable
sudo chmod +x ubuntu-22.04-lts-vpn-server.sh
sudo ./ubuntu-22.04-lts-vpn-server.sh
Choose the default options
Ensure you open the set port on your security groups > inbound rules on azure
Once a client file is created copy it to your device
Use openvpn client software and choose the file to connect to the vpn